I"§<h2 id="change-salary-through-pay-proposal">Change Salary Through Pay Proposal</h2>

<p><strong>STEP-1</strong>: Select pay projection from list and right click on it. Select <strong>Browse Pay Projection</strong>.</p>

<p><img src="http://docs.risersoft.com/hrmnirvana/ImagesExt/image8_139.jpg" alt="" /></p>

<p><strong>STEP-2</strong>: Click on <strong>Current Proposal -&gt; Staff</strong>. Select the employee and right click on it. Select <strong>Edit Pay Proposal Salary</strong>. Pay Proposal form will appear.</p>

<p><img src="http://docs.risersoft.com/hrmnirvana/ImagesExt/image8_140.jpg" alt="" /></p>

<p><strong>STEP-3</strong>: Enter details and click on <strong>Define</strong> button. Employee Salary form will appear.</p>

<p><img src="http://docs.risersoft.com/hrmnirvana/ImagesExt/image8_141.jpg" alt="" /></p>

<p><strong>STEP-4</strong>: Edit details and click on <strong>Calculate and Save</strong> button.</p>

<p><strong>STEP-5</strong>: If you want to apply salary changes in group then again right click on employee in browser view and select <strong>Edit Enforce Pay proposal</strong>.</p>

<p><img src="http://docs.risersoft.com/hrmnirvana/ImagesExt/image8_142.jpg" alt="" /></p>

<p><strong>STEP-6</strong>: Select pay period and click on <strong>OK</strong>. When enforce process completed, Enforced message will appear.</p>

<p><img src="http://docs.risersoft.com/hrmnirvana/ImagesExt/image8_143.png" alt="" /></p>
